drm/amd/display: Add DCN2 OPP

Add support to program the DCN2 OPP (Output Plane Processing)

HW Blocks:

    +-------+
    |  OPP  |
    +-------+
        |
        v
    +--------+
    |  OPTC  |
    +--------+
        |
        v
    +--------+       +--------+
    |  DIO   |       |  DCCG  |
    +--------+       +--------+

